cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as document search, recommendation, and question answering, which are typically covered under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The use of word embeddings and unsupervised learning methods further supports the inclusion of this paper in these sub-categories.
